metadata.description:
when I was little, my elders used to ask me, does anyone who reads a lot know more or knows anyone who travels a lot..of course reading is very useful..but travel enriches people a lot..I love to travel..  
in 2020 we visited malta..it is a very historical place with very beautiful landscapes..this beach bar is a very popular spot in malta..its name is "1926 beach club"..this place is owned by "hotel 1926" which is only a few hundred meters away and its guests can enter here for free..others have to enter with ticket..it is dazzling with its infinity pool next to the mediterranean sea..  
this is a compilation of 2 photos. both from malta, dates mainly from photo "1926"

1926  
sliema, malta | 2020  
limited to 19 editions  
dji mavic air  + polar pro filter  
3508 x 4961
